name: Glass Sculptures
description:
i know some models already have a good glass sculpture support, but many others, just don't, this is why i'm making this.

use:

a glasssculpture of [], transparent, translucent, reflections, [style, etc]

if you are getting weird close ups, try using model at 0.6.

tested on DreamShaper and Grapefruit models

Consider donating pls

modelVersions.name: v2.0 completely redone dataset
modelVersions.description:
fixed artifacts issues, now you can even force model up to 1.5 without any cuts or weird things on the final generation.

this took 8 attempts, 4100 steps and 41 imgs to make
